    public abstract class WebRTC
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.WebMarkupContainer
    A WebRTC component to create a video conference based on SimpleWebRTC. http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/webrtc/basics/
    https://github.com/andyet/signalmaster
    https://github.com/HenrikJoreteg/SimpleWebRTC
    https://github.com/HenrikJoreteg/webrtc.js
    Author:
    Tobias Soloschenko
